		Type of Resource:
        </div>
        <div class="FormRowData" style= "margin-left:25px">
   		<br/>
        <%=  select(:content, :content_resource_type_id, ContentResourceType.all(:order => "name").collect{|d| [d.name, d.id]}) %>
        <span style="color:#C73914;">*</span>        
		
		</div>
